    <title type="html"><![CDATA[The amazing interior designs of BRICKS Amsterdam]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.analogsenses.com/2014/11/25/the-amazing-interior-designs-of-bricks-amsterdam/"/>
    <updated>2014-11-25T13:15:58+01:00</updated>
    <id>http://www.analogsenses.com/2014/11/25/the-amazing-interior-designs-of-bricks-amsterdam</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>BRICKS Amsterdam is an Amsterdam-based interior design studio created by James van der Velden. They have some incredible projects, including <a href="http://www.bricksamsterdam.com/project/garage-loft-amsterdam/">this stunning industrial loft</a> that they created in what used to be an old garage:</p>

<p class="extra-width"><img src="https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7560/15873604691_f9507e8eb2_h.jpg" alt="Garage Loft by BRICKS Amsterdam"/></p>




<p class="extra-width"><img src="https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8575/15689828587_ed2f61a832_h.jpg" alt="Garage Loft by BRICKS Amsterdam"/></p>




<p class="extra-width"><img src="https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7531/15688086318_5cde998b52_h.jpg" alt="Garage Loft by BRICKS Amsterdam"/></p>




<p class="extra-width"><img src="https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7546/15689829237_e1f5e6c109_h.jpg" alt="Garage Loft by BRICKS Amsterdam"/></p>


<p>Also, check out <a href="http://www.bricksamsterdam.com/project/loft-amsterdam/">this other loft</a>, comparing before and after pictures. It&rsquo;s just as impressive, if not more.</p>

<p>I love how some talented designers can truly transform a space beyond recognition. It&rsquo;s an incredible skill that requires a unique blend of really good taste, impeccable craft and a very vivid imagination.</p>
